  "independentDerivation": "手工推导：|v1×v2| = 5×10⁻¹⁰ ≤ 容差界 ≈ 10⁻⁹ → 近似平行；点积 1 > 0 → same-direction。cos θ = 1/√(1+2.5×10⁻¹⁹)，双精度下舍入为 1，θ ≈ 0°。容差路径必须记录 tolerance。",
  "validationRules": [
    "cosine-within-bounds",
    "angle-range",
    "angle-classification"
  ]
}
